# Liabilities Loans Deposits Amount

## identifier
de14711

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for liabilities generated from loans taken out and deposits received. This item is to be determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.LoansDeposits.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.28
- period=instant
